Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumohon, Akane Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.38,0:00:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Cuma kau yang bisa perankan\Ntokoh utama wanitanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun, memaksa sekali\Npara kakak kelas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada orang lain\Nyang bisa memainkan peran ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami mohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa tak lakukan saja untuk mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tampil di kompetisi teater\Nterdengar keren.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Untuk apa kau lakukan itu, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, rumornya ternyata benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pasti Ranma Saotome,\Nyang memakai kostum perempuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ini bukan kostum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Tunggu, bukan kostum?\N- Aku tak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa salto di udara\Ndan menghancurkan batu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Dia bisa pelajari trik dalam sekejap…\N- Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tak mau melakukannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bisa jadi tokoh utamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa temanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seorang ahli bela diri, seorang pegulat,\Natau gadis asasin berpakaian hitam?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.02,0:01:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terlahir untuk peran itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Coba ulangi ucapanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.02,0:01:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, jawabannya tidak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak adalah tidak,\Nberapa kali pun kau bertanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.16,0:01:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, Ranma Saotome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai hari ini, kau adalah Juliet kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}O Romeo, di mana gerangan dirimu, Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.21,0:01:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau mau melakukannya untuk kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.25,0:01:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tatewaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Panggil aku Romeo, Juliet Jelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau pikir dirimu Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Formulir pendaftaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku sudah masuk klub ini,\Nsudah sepantasnya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku yang dipilih sebagai tokoh utama!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.12,0:02:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Jika aku memerankan Romeo,\Naku bisa bicara dengan Akane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Kami cuma perlu satu Romeo…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Happosai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.34,0:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahwa aku harus berperan sebagai Romeo\Ndi usia senjaku ini…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi jika aku jadi Romeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}aku bisa beradegan cinta dengan Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya Juliet cukup populer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun, semoga berhasil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku bisa berperan sebagai Juliet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku harus berusaha keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Wah, kali ini Akane akan perankan Juliet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tunggu, "kali ini"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Saat SD, Akane memerankan Romeo\Ndi drama sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Dia cocok memerankannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku? Memerankan Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Kau cocok sekali, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau jadi Romeo, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti cocok!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menderita…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aksimu bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kau hebat!\N- Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akane, kau kuat sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi yang kuinginkan…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah memakai gaun cantik\Ndan memerankan Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak sanggup untuk menolak…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.47,0:05:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kali ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan memerankan Juliet,\Nperan yang sejak dulu kuimpikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini saatnya latihan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adegan balkon dari {\i1}Romeo dan Juliet{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan makan di dekat telingaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang, izinkan aku bertanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tahu isi cerita\Ndari drama {\i1}Romeo dan Juliet{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Ini drama tentang seorang samurai\Nbertato bunga sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet, tuangkan yang banyak untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.05,0:05:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini mustahil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak akan pernah memenangkan\Nkompetisi teater jika begini…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita tak akan dapat hadiahnya,\Nkunjungan VIP ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:06:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa kau bilang kunjungan ke Tiongkok?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunjungan ke Tiongkok!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tiket emasku untuk ke Jusenkyo\Ndan mencari Mata Air Lelaki Tenggelam!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kuperingatkan kau, Juliet adalah peranku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh, aku pun tak mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.29,0:06:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan dengan itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau tentukan pemeran Romeo sekarang juga?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menghadapimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kita tak boleh mengandalkan kekerasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena ini untuk drama, apa kita tentukan\Npemeran Romeo di atas panggung?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti orang terakhir yang masih berdiri\Npada akhir pementasan…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan ditetapkan sebagai Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Battle royale{\i0}, ya? Menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sabar menantikan hari pementasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau rusak peluangku jadi Juliet\Npada pementasan yang layak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya berantakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Akane-ku yang malang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Semua ini sudah berantakan\Nsebelum aku terlibat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Apa dia begitu menantikannya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jadi, siapa si Romeo ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja dia seorang samurai\Nyang muncul dari persik.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Lalu, dia makan sebuah apel beracun…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mohon berkumpul di gimnasium{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}untuk Kompetisi Teater SMA.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Ranma Saotome tak bisa ditemukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.90,0:07:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku belum melihatnya sejak kemarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kira-kira di mana dia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.49,0:07:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang berarti…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.74,0:07:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet Jelita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan serahkan peran Romeo kepadaku,\NTatewaki Kuno, tanpa bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar Ranma memang pengecut.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tenang saja, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan jadi Romeo yang sempurna untukmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar tua bangka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranma…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau masih hidup?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pikirmu rantai ringkih ini
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah cukup untuk menghentikanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah, Ranma.\NJadi, kau bisa berperan sebagai Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.94,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku penggemar beratmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.32,0:08:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kucurahkan hatiku\Nuntuk membuat kostum panggung ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga berhasil memerankan Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu terlalu meyakinkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Dengan tersingkirnya Ranma, aku bisa…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, tapi aku sudah punya pasangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau permainkan hatiku seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dasar bodoh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, Ranma.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kau tahu cara berakting?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berkesempatan pergi ke Tiongkok\Ndengan memerankan si Romeo ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengar, Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku akan menjadi Romeo yang sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau fokus saja\Nuntuk menjadi Juliet yang sempurna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranma…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa hubungan Romeo dan Juliet?\N- Ayah-anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.21,0:09:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baca dulu ceritanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Terima kasih sudah menunggu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Pementasan terakhir\Ndari Kompetisi Teater SMA{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}adalah{\i0} Romeo dan Juliet\N{\i1}dari Klub Drama SMA Furinkan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}O Romeo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di mana gerangan dirimu, Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus, Akane Tendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Romeo dan Juliet jatuh cinta\Npada pandangan pertama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan tetapi, sejoli terikat takdir ini\Npunya keluarga yang berseteru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo datang secara diam-diam…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, aku Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini konyol! Aku Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku!\N- Diam, itu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kata siapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.00,0:09:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini waktunya kuis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.84,0:09:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Siapakah Romeo yang asli?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet Jelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.35,0:10:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku tak akan menang bertarung,\Njadi aku menyamar di balkon…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini amat disayangkan…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ra… Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa diam lama sekali…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan, itu jeda dramatis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita bisa merasakan cinta\Nyang mereka berdua miliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Wahai Romeo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.42,0:10:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa kau tahu dialogmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo memeluk Juliet dengan erat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kuduga akan seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.52,0:10:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengarkan, Ranma. Ikuti saja instruksiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Juliet Jelita.\N- Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:10:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menikahimu\Ndan mewarisi perguruan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Perguruan?\N- Dia bicara apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sekarang, berciuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.08,0:11:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ini saat yang ditunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Mereka sungguh akan berciuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Itu luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Apa?\N- Bukan, cuma pura-pura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan menyebar ide konyol!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kedua keluarga sudah menyetujuinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, berciumanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, berciuman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan main-main!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli jika ini cuma untuk pentas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau mencium Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak mau menciumnya, tak akan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak bisa begini!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Romeo dan Juliet{\i0} macam apa\Nyang tak punya adegan cinta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku sudah tak peduli lagi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelas menolak melakukan adegan cinta\Nmembuatmu tak layak untuk peran itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Enyahlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh, aku cuma…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ingin aku mencium\NTatewaki-senpai atau Kakek?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku kecupan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.97,0:12:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan ganggu aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Juliet terpukul kesedihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bagaimana nasib cinta mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutunjukkan adegan cinta\Nyang tak akan terlupakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Ranma bodoh.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Pementasan ini benar-benar berantakan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jangan menyerah, Akane!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakak Kasumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.83,0:12:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat betapa kau mendambakan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak bisa menyerah\Nkarena hal seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia benar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Memerankan Juliet\Nadalah impian masa kecilku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak peduli siapa yang memerankan Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini kau paham, Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Romeo!\N- Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku tak bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.94,0:12:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet Jelita, akhirnya kita akan menikah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Juliet malang\Ntelah menjadi mempelai dedemit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang kau sebut dedemit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wahai Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habiskan! Inilah toas pernikahan kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.87,0:13:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa pemeran Juliet diganti\Ndi tengah pertunjukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku agak mabuk…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo, kau kuat sekali minum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.42,0:13:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Mau kuberi hadiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berikan bramu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dapat satu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet Jelita!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo, betapa aku mendambakanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga, Juliet Jelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bebas alkohol, jangan khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini adalah embun cinta\Nyang membasahi pipi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lawan aku, Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.91,0:13:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari berjumpa lagi\Njika salah satu dari kita selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, kau menantangku\Nuntuk beradu pedang cinta…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keinginan tulusmu telah mencapaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terima duel ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Aku tak bilang begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bersihkan telingamu\Ndan dengarkan baik-baik
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa yang kukatakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kenapa bertarung?\N- Cintamu kurasakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Kenapa bukan kawin lari?\N- Kenapa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan menikah, sekarang juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.73,0:14:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa terburu-buru, Romeo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lompatlah ke pelukanku jika kau mau hidup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Juliet Jelita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir aku terpojok?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.21,0:14:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Juliet yang malang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Dia mati di usia amat belia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau jatuh untuk menyelamatkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Inilah ciuman perpisahan kita…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet itu palsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet! Jadi, kau masih hidup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melawanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah. Jika aku menang,\Nkau akan melamarku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, bangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau pasti kalah dariku dalam adu pedang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekalian saja kau mengajakku berpacaran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, ini saatnya adegan cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sekarang, ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar Romeo tukang selingkuh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ranma, itu tidak adil! Akulah Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebegitu inginnya kau mencium Tatewaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, jangan ikut campur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.90,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku harus menangkan kompetisi ini\Ndan pergi ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menjijikkan sekali walau ada lakbannya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku bahagia, Gadis Berkepang…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itu sungguh momen yang romantis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dapat dua!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, kini adegan cinta sudah selesai…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet, pertunjukkan harus diteruskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenci itukah kau kepadaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau mencium Tatewaki-senpai, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kini aku benar-benar paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terserah. Aku mau pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, kenapa kau begitu kesal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa. Aku sudah selesai di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah aku berkorban, kini kau mau pergi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak peduli.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku memakai lakban.\N- Itu mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terserah.\N- Mereka bertengkar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Maafkan aku, Akane Tendo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak akan menyangkal\Nbahwa aku mencium Gadis Berkepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}- Kau tak menciumnya.\N- Aku menciumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kalau begitu, jelaskan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Itu kenang-kenangan dari ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dengar itu, Akane?\NLakban ini adalah bukti tak terbantahkan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semoga saja kau suka obat bius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu untuk apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Akhirnya aku bisa bicara dengan Akane.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maju selangkah lagi,\Nmaka kuhabisi nyawa Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Apa?\N- Ayo, Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan pergi jauh bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak akan adil\Njika aku cuma mencium Gadis Berkepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus menciummu juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.00,0:17:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Sudah kubilang, kau tak menciumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akane, bangun.\NKita harus selesaikan pementasannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Akan tetapi, Juliet tidak terbangun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Juliet tertidur lelap.\NHanya satu hal yang dapat membangunkannya
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan itu adalah ciuman dari Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kenapa kau terus membahas soal ciuman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingatlah kunjungan ke Tiongkok.\NItu adalah permintaan dari juri tamu kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kau cium, kau menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sponsor?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ranma, ciumlah dia\Njika kau mau pergi ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku mau pergi, tapi…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti seharusnya\Ntak ada masalah di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan keras kepala dan beri dia ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.93,0:18:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Jika aku bisa melewati ini,\Naku akan dapat tiket ke Tiongkok.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ini demi menjadi pria lagi! Baiklah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.48,0:18:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Tiket ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Hentikan itu, kau mengalihkan perhatianku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akui kekalahanmu, Romeo palsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika memang ada cinta,\Nsatu ciuman di muka umum tak akan…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lebih pemalu daripadamu, paham?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lebih memilih menolak kunjungan VIP\Nke Tiongkok daripada mencium Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau pasti amat membenci Juliet-ku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ranma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.22,0:19:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Dasar bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tak akan jadi masalah\Njika aku tak menyukainya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.35,0:19:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Romeo…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kapan kau terbangun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Aku akan mengirimmu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau tak perlu sampai sejauh itu…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.87,0:19:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau paham, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kau bahkan tak mau berpura-pura\Nuntuk pementasan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}{\i1}Dia manis sekali…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini momen penentunya.\NKita sudah mendapatkan juaranya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Bagaimana? Bukankah itu meyakinkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau masih cemberut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia menipuku. Dia benar-benar…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, andai saja tak ada lakban itu\Ndi antara kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, aku cuma bercanda.\NAtau memang kau sebodoh itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sama sekali tidak manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimanapun,\Nkau seharusnya berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat diriku, kau menangkan\Nkunjungan ke Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, aku tahu. Kau berisik sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Kalian pulang larut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kunjungan dari Tiongkok sudah dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sudah dimulai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Ranma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Perkenalkan Tn. Ryoko. Dia dari Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas kunjungan VIP ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada semacam miskomunikasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kuisi lagi gelasnya, Tn. Ryoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ya ampun, Ranma tampak kelelahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Mungkin dia akan bangun\Njika kau beri ciuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih baik jika dia dibiarkan tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Terjemahan subtitle oleh Rio Wibowo
